### Override Collection Admin UI Settings

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/PLUGIN-DEVELOPMENT.md

This code shows how to modify the admin UI configuration for a collection. It allows for setting properties like 'group', 'hidden', and 'defaultColumns', influencing how the collection appears and behaves in the Payload admin panel.

```typescript
// From plugin-redirects
