### Configure Payload Image Size Admin Panel Display Options (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/upload/overview.mdx

This TypeScript configuration defines an image size named 'thumbnail' with specific `admin` options to control its visibility and behavior within the Payload Admin Panel's list view. It shows how to disable groupBy options, list columns, and list filters for this size. This is useful for hiding large or rarely used image sizes from the UI while keeping them available via API.

```ts
{
  name: 'thumbnail',
  width: 400,
  height: 300,
  admin: {
    disableGroupBy: true, // hide from list view groupBy options
    disableListColumn: true, // hide from list view columns
    disableListFilter: true // hide from list view filters
  }
}
```

